# GitHub Personal Access Token
# Get yours at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Classic token scopes: repo, read:user
# Fine-grained token permissions:
#   - Metadata: read
#   - Administration: read/write (repo settings, collaborators, deletion)
#   - Contents: read/write (code search and file updates)
#   - Pull requests: read/write
#   - Issues: read/write (issues and comments)
#   - Actions: read/write (workflows, runs, artifacts)
GITHUB_TOKEN=
